---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-3 px-4 py-8 text-sm text-zinc-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8 dark:text-zinc-400">
        <p>“我们被我们塑造的东西所塑造着。”</p>
        <p>
            © 2025–{year} 芷夏
            <span class="mx-1.5 text-zinc-300 dark:text-zinc-700" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
            <a
                class="transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-orange-600 dark:hover:text-orange-400"
                href="https://github.com/zxzxovo"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
            >GitHub</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</footer>
